Package: glkterm
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: NCurses.h Implementation of the Glk API.
 This is an implementation of the Glk library which runs in a terminal window,
 using the curses.h library for screen control, written by Andrew Plotkin.
